# Zice platform invariants

## Ticket prefixes (docs/tickets in zice-platform-dev)

| Prefix | Repo |
|--------|------|
| `C*` | zice-core |
| `F*` | zice-frontend |
| `A*` | zice-agent (+ related frontend) |
| `L*` | League features (often core + frontend) |
| `X*` | Cross-repo |

## Data & security

- **Multi-tenant context:** API calls use `x-org-slug` (and validated org membership). Do not bypass tenant middleware.
- **Auth:** Supabase issues JWTs; Go services validate JWTs — they do not implement password storage.
- **RLS:** Platform tables use PostgreSQL RLS in migrations. New tables need policies in the same migration.
- **Soft delete:** Prefer `deleted_at` + restore endpoints; default lists exclude deleted rows.

## Cross-repo changes

When adding a service boundary, env var, or migration path, update **zice-platform-dev** `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` and the relevant `AGENTS.md` (templates under `docs/templates/AGENTS/`).
